## Stack

- Entry: `app/javascript/application.js` (Turbo, ActiveStorage, Stimulus, components)
- Stimulus controllers: `app/javascript/controllers/*_controller.js`
- MVM wallet code: TypeScript under `app/javascript/mvm/`
- Built with esbuild (`esbuild.config.js`); styles via Tailwind (`yarn build:css`)

## Conventions

- Register Stimulus controllers in `app/javascript/controllers/index.js`
- Use `@hotwired/turbo-rails` and `@rails/request.js` for server interactions
- Prefer existing utilities in `app/javascript/utils/` (toast, notify, uploader)
- Run `yarn lint-check` (Prettier) on touched `app/javascript/**/*.{tsx,ts,js,gql}` files

## Avoid

- Adding a second bundler or framework alongside esbuild/Stimulus without discussion
- Direct DOM manipulation when a Stimulus controller pattern already exists
- Committing built assets in `app/assets/builds/` unless the project already does for a specific reason
